Then he kind of has a character arc similar to 40-something Peter Parker in 'Into the Spiderverse' Out of shape and not in his best headspace but still trying to help and ultimately he gets back to where he needs to be in life.

Then he continues as a major supporting character in any sequels. Kind of the veteran presence like Arnie has been in most of the recent movies.
